7:54.166893421Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program log: Instruction: CreatePlayerProfile\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.170878630Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program 11111111111111111111111111111111 invoke [2]\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.170929296Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program 11111111111111111111111111111111 success\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.172627421Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM consumed 9809 of 200000 compute units\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.172652755Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM success\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.194393796Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM invoke [1]\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.194619171Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program log: Instruction: CreatePlayerProfile\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.201735713Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program 11111111111111111111111111111111 invoke [2]\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.201794588Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Allocate: account Address { address: 2Au3HzGRLiGFnpcdR2G8ncQA8ccfv1Hh7bGVLGmyQr7j, base: None } already in use\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.201804755Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program 11111111111111111111111111111111 failed: custom program error: 0x0\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.201812546Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM consumed 7799 of 200000 compute units\n[2026-02-26T08:27:54.201818755Z DEBUG solana_runtime::message_processor::stable_log] Program dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM failed: custom program error: 0x0\n      ✔ rejects double profile creation (114ms)\n\n\n  31 passing (4s)","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
